nh/Ho%C3%A0ng-giang-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9/poem-Odb9V6tAFfDKI4hpG4UNxg">Hoàng giang dạ vũ - 黃江夜雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97/S%C6%A1n-l%C3%A2u-xuy-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch-t%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%95-quy-Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%B9ng/poem-P09GaFh7khruSpueaeBKvw">Sơn lâu xuy địch tống Trương Thúc Hổ quy Ngô Tùng - 山樓吹笛送張叔虎歸吳淞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97/author-qvR5jQ1KJBBzJ7wiP-fcNA">Tiền Đỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tuy-L%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%AA-Ng%C6%B0ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-UxwuY5P_Juk2od7kmlzOjw">Tặng Lê Ngưng Phủ - 贈黎凝甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tuy-L%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-B6iyJCR5kCh5mPMgMOCH1Q">Tuy Lý Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%AD-An-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA/poem-3EtEYotauMJWOh4Awz0OaQ">Tuyệt cú - 絕句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%AD-An-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-Qyf_BWcnPQcxj6qpqNzzzA">Chí An thiền sư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
